Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾有一群相互憎恨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遍地屍野 靈魂四散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽絆被利刃斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泥濘於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心靈在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赴死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了後可別怨我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怨的話 就去怨德川家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去怨駿府的大御所 那個天下第二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及 為自己身為甲賀之人而怨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一天終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:05:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦…之…介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手上有劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那悲鳴聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餵你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那發什麼抖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如真有那萬一之事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去拿劍 朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 必須殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也必須殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也許能夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在 雙目失明了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也…看不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與{\fnmingliu\fs22\be1}卍{\r}谷眾的廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這雙眼 復明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀 就剩我一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀也 只餘我一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去拿劍 朧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 您為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您為何 下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀…{\fnmingliu\fs22\be1}卍{\r}谷的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要背叛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女人騙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鍔隱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦…之介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…與您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能安度之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經哪都…沒有了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任你一人活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣…不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒息…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想過要傷害誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀弦之介來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人 又死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天膳是不死忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是都知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來人 把他扶起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將那頭顱放回原位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是關係著竹千代少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我阿福 以及你們所有人命運的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幻婆婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心藥師寺天膳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你還沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他操縱著不死妙術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且並非忍法之奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的體內寄宿著某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說 那黑幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我出生很久以前的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒確認過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若如我想 真是那東西的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幻婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了些無聊的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對生活在今後的你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不需要知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也老了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幻婆婆
