Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙瞳復明了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在朧背後的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樓梯…那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對生活在今後的你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不需要知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀{\fnmingliu\fs22\be1}卍{\r}谷一族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀鍔隱一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌握著那恐怖忍法秘術的雙方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長年的宿怨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對生活在今後的你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不需要知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想過要傷害誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死…死掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…朧…朧啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方才天膳所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確…我身後匿藏著…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受了傷…無法動彈的甲賀之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻是伊賀的 羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候你還在講什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去通知服部半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去備馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在雙忍仲裁半藏大人的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異議了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異議…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿生之初的完結
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天轉地移
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人污穢的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墜入那青暗之深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相隨相逝之奈何彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.34,0:23:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配予絕妙的心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法結合的悲戀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來生再相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來世再實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basilisk 甲賀忍法帖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終回
